steps.html_instructions: Head southwest on S Tryon St toward E 4th St
Turn left to merge onto I-85 S toward Gastonia
Take exit 10B to merge onto US-74 W toward Kings Mountain/Shelby
Keep left at the fork to continue on US-74 W
Take exit 393 for I-640 W/US-25W toward I-75 N/Lexington
Exit 393 turns slightly left and becomes I-640 W/US-25W N
Keep left at the fork to continue on I-64 W, follow signs for Frankfort/Louisvile
Take exit 5B for 3rd St/River Rd toward Downtown

Turn right onto S 5th St
Destination will be on the right
